                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Richmond</placeName>\n                <date>17 March 1836</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Yesterday I received your letter on the subject<lb/> of your\n                discourses; I will do my best to promote your views<lb/> but I fear very little\n                success will attend my endeavours I<lb/> am confined to the house and mostly to my\n                chamber in<lb/> Ten weeks<add>?</add> I rode out twice without any favourable<lb/>\n                result—perhaps when the weather becomes mild I may<lb/> find relief from moderate\n                exercise. I will try and get<lb/>\n                <persName>Jacob Levy</persName> the parnass to interest himself in procuring\n                subscriptions<lb/> my family desire their regards—not knowing when a private<lb/>\n                <sic>oppy</sic> may present &amp; wishing that you should think<lb/> great regard I\n                am Dr Sir yr friend</p>\n            <p>\n                <persName role=\"author\">Jacob Mordecai</persName>\n            </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p34q7r95p/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
